title: ‘White Wolf and the Dragon Queen’
body:
Well…. I woke up today and saw that the fic had reached 2220 kudos on AO3, and that is amazing. When I started writing it, I could never have imagined that so many people would enjoy it.

So thank you all for reading and leaving kudos and comments. Every comment makes the headaches and bouts of writer’s block so worth it

summary:
Gendry‘s age in the show was just recently noted on the GoT wikia page, it wasn’t there before 🤔
So he‘s three years older than...
body:
Gendry‘s age in the show was just recently noted on the GoT wikia page, it wasn’t there before 🤔

So he‘s three years older than Arya in the show which makes the age difference even smaller than the one in the books which is about 4-5 years. And show!Gendry is also 2 years younger than Jon. Interesting.
